1a. Create a program that asks the user to enter their name and their age. Print out a message addressed to them that tells them the year that they will turn 100 years old

name=input("Enter your name :- ")
age=int(input("Enter your age :- "))
birth_year=2022-age
future_year=birth_year+100
print(name+"you will be 100 years old in"+str(future_year))
